{"tid":2122754,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"豁免檢疫人數仲多過強制檢疫人數，抗乜撚疫。。。。。。","createTime":"2020-07-24T07:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T10:58:36.000Z","uid":7439,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9894061071b070bcc0547c5c9c56a6c33ba4b5","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毛孟靜議員的提問和保安局局長李家超的書面答覆：<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/08/P2020070800810.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F08%2FP2020070800810.htm&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6FDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=16cd8ae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/08/P2020070800810.htm</a><br />\n根據衞生署提供的資料，截至二○二○年五月，於各出入境管制站向獲豁免人士（包括根據第599C及第599E章獲豁免的人士）發出醫學監察通知書的數字如下：<br />\n月份 於各運作中的出入境管制站向獲豁免人士<br />\n發出醫學監察通知書數目<br />\n二○二○年二月 93 602<br />\n二○二○年三月 39 211<br />\n二○二○年四月 36 039<br />\n二○二○年五月 40 220</blockquote><br />\n二至五月合計：209072<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n政府發言人稱，各出入境管制站5月和6月（截至21日）分別最少有4萬和3.2萬人次獲免檢疫入境，但未有提供相關檢測病毒的數字。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">即係二到六月都至少24萬豁免檢疫入境</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>陳沛然議員的提問和食物及衞生局局長陳肇始教授的書面答覆：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/06/P2020050600316.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F06%2FP2020050600316.htm&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6FDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=03690c74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/06/P2020050600316.htm</a><br />\n截至二○二○年五月四日，衞生署根據第599C章及第599E章，分別向103 543名由內地、台灣及澳門抵港人士，以及69 685名由外國抵港人士發出強制檢疫令。</blockquote><br />\n2月8日至5月4日合計發出173228張強制檢疫令<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">之後？冇人問、咪冇人答囉</span></span>"},{"pid":"115a42b95fb4b63e612656553b0872be2947dc9c","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"海事處證實逾1萬船員獲豁免檢疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68612ab59cf53d9384263e0644c7b6893d31229b","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"強制檢疫人數永遠都冇人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳沛然議員成功取得中國肺炎檢疫令數字：中台澳103543、外國69685<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2004285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2004285</a><br />\n<br />\nff系列 - 接受強制檢疫的人數<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1941356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1941356</a><br />\n<br />\n張竹君：我笠撚硬水 你今世都搵唔撚到599C名單架啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fkiLuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fkiLuS</a><br />\n<br />\n強制檢疫人數係反送中被捕人數幾多倍？截止上周已經有七倍............<br />\n(截至五月至少二十倍)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1938393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1938393</a>"},{"pid":"38c1a8655d38a6097cdc195e30bbbb9267265313","tid":2122754,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497b57c869f1452799ec8a3ebb8c403260729b68","tid":2122754,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0df27ff74d5510ed6f39a185cb6292b53b3f49","tid":2122754,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b4c921a6968cf04a490675453df930601fef95","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"記者問個問題都2分鐘，咪俾人遊花園囉<br />\n簡單啲啦：豁免有幾多、強制有幾多<br />\n<br />\n你手頭上冇，咪日日問到有囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔撚知，叫個知嘅答囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00bed9eb044495606896b34d678fec0c00a51b8","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat_menu.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fmessage_from_us%2Fstat_menu.html&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6FDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=98f76d3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/message_from_us/stat_menu.html</a><br />\n入境事務處嘅「出入境人次統計數字」<br />\n得按日計冇按月計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都係唔想人知唔想人查啫，<br />\n唔想人知申請禁制令囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a9ef29220e9d2773c4401518be7b91c08d312c","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"根據教育局公佈的跨境學童最新數字顯示，全港有25,576 名跨境學童，當中分別有7,602名中學生及17,974名小學生，而北區有11,609名跨境學童，佔總數超過四成。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e72cfc7a2801f1e64fa10bfdd2a33557e39a193","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:04:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202007/08/P2020070800810_345150_1_1594212870909.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F08%2FP2020070800810_345150_1_1594212870909.pdf&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6FDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=1e388e42\" target=\"_blank\">https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202007/08/P2020070800810_345150_1_1594212870909.pdf</a><br />\n5月<br />\n香港居民 75 547<br />\n內地訪客 7 649<br />\n其他國家 5 263<br />\n<br />\n5月出入境人次八萬八，豁免檢疫入境都四萬啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9501686a5c2df78c8fc5af4b425c884cb6962b49","tid":2122754,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fdcbcb1c39c4f8e076a4ef06878dbe897185d6","tid":2122754,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4ee809d4f9d5e8b55a40c3ff2b2e58082d7454","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42fdcbcb1c39c4f8e076a4ef06878dbe897185d6","tid":2122754,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:43:09.000Z","msg":"統計處：54萬香港居民逗留廣東省，其中12萬60歲或以上<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fJgRRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fJgRRS</a>"},{"pid":"b326f4303fbb895b96adce28d902794e31e52ad6","tid":2122754,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adf3b199ed20186da5d3af00f229f34d8bf1952","tid":2122754,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"唔爆多d點有籍口取消個選舉整個臨立會呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5be30ecde3d06c104da5e7dd765c61ac978b36","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6adf3b199ed20186da5d3af00f229f34d8bf1952","tid":2122754,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"唔爆多d點有籍口取消個選舉整個臨立會呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"599C延至九月七日，唔撚投了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4047e453cbe2c7ab0ab67f4efbcc54e1ad55db70","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"【逾29萬人過去數月入境香港後獲豁免強制檢疫14日】<br />\n<br />\n衞生署回本覆本台查詢時表示，當局6月於各出入境管制站，向45953名獲豁免檢疫的人士發出醫學監察通知書，較5月份多5733人，亦是自3月以來最多的月份。本月截至22日，則向39584人發出有關通知書。<br />\n<br />\n保安局本月8日書面回覆立法會議員提問時透露，政府由2月至5月一共向約20萬人發出通知書。換言之，<span class=\"red\">由2月至前日，有29萬4千多人入境後毋須接受強制檢疫14日</span>，但要接受14天醫學監察，期間須佩戴口罩和每天量度體溫兩次。<br />\n<br />\n現時有33類人士抵港後獲豁免檢疫，包括跨境貨車司機、機組人員、船員、政府人員、為香港供應個人防護裝備相關人員、在內地從事生產作業的香港企業人員、在內地提供專業服務的建造業人員、在內地進行物流活動人員等等。<br />\n<br />\n本台向衞生署查詢分類數字，以了解過去數月獲豁免檢疫人士中，有多少屬於船員、機組人員或其他類別。衞生署回應時指，沒有備存分項數字。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #新型肺炎"},{"pid":"f8ed80c957888ac293ae1b7cec68092594eeefcc","tid":2122754,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"孫兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597c16b25393fe837cf8e8e6d4c6adf977fefee1","tid":2122754,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T17:15:39.000Z","msg":"資料王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fde1393fa01c87bdb65026d245bc0b862c953a","tid":2122754,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T18:49:35.000Z","msg":"推啦 屌"},{"pid":"906db0201c1657fb0d948940ad116fe88835ec6e","tid":2122754,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T18:49:57.000Z","msg":"整張圖。sd去藍屍gp"},{"pid":"1a2e0db59277fd6bd1b8f7860ef2b5a566991d26","tid":2122754,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T19:09:36.000Z","msg":"樓主啲post 有營養過cctoy 啲post 十萬九千倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892d457bc0f70844fd1856f2ecef7f65e33bcf3d","tid":2122754,"uid":108631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T19:39:41.000Z","msg":"一個比呢個政府管 一日香港唔會有運行"},{"pid":"c3a56566638e18a4e22c5cc768a1f9efe0b02759","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a2e0db59277fd6bd1b8f7860ef2b5a566991d26","tid":2122754,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T19:09:36.000Z","msg":"樓主啲post 有營養過cctoy 啲post 十萬九千倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b47a37b1ae57045af1aa92fbc8e9810ed19ad06","tid":2122754,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8b4c921a6968cf04a490675453df930601fef95","tid":2122754,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"記者問個問題都2分鐘，咪俾人遊花園囉<br />\n簡單啲啦：豁免有幾多、強制有幾多<br />\n<br />\n你手頭上冇，咪日日問到有囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔撚知，叫個知嘅答囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite